data.text:
Provides a new entry to Preferences --> General --> Keys (IntelliJ IDEA)

The supported shortcuts can be seen here https://github.com/IntelliJIdeaKeymap4Eclipse/IntelliJIdeaKeymap4Eclipse

Work in progress, not tested on Linux.

Contributions are welcomed. Please provide bug and feature reports via the GitHub page.

Eclipse Versions: 2021-03 (4.19), 2020-12 (4.18), 2020-09 (4.17), 2020-06 (4.16), 2020-03 (4.15), 2019-12 (4.14), 2019-09 (4.13), 2019-06 (4.12), 2019-03 (4.11), 2018-12 (4.10), 2018-09 (4.9), Photon (4.8), Oxygen (4.7), Neon (4.6)

Platform Support: Windows, Mac, Linux/GTK

Development Status: Mature
